import React from "react";
import { Button, Control, Input, Field, Label } from "react-bulma-components";

function BookForm() {
  return (
    <>
      <Field>
        <Control>
          <Label>Name</Label>
          <Input name="name" value="Hermes" />
        </Control>
      </Field>
      <Field>
        <Control>
          <Label>Password</Label>
          <Input name="password" type="password" value="12345" />
        </Control>
      </Field>
      <Button.Group>
        <Button
          fullwidth
          rounded
          color="primary"
          onClick={() => console.log(form)}
        >
          Login
        </Button>
      </Button.Group>
    </>
  );
}

export default BookForm;
